{"tid":2309863,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"【兩性】第一次出街男仔一定要畀哂錢？ 日本少女唔係咁睇","createTime":"2020-12-03T00:40:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-03T01:12:34.000Z","uid":65328,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d805492fd54c2fa46223d287e3bf243223626f6e","tid":2309863,"uid":65328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T00:40:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.menclub.hk/mobile/article/article.php?cat=thezone&amp;aid=25388\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.menclub.hk%2Fmobile%2Farticle%2Farticle.php%3Fcat%3Dthezone%26aid%3D25388&d=u42ujRIT%2FE%2FeodHrCKN%2BOZriIWEbfV0cuvPRs67P9cA%3D&h=8024a885\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.menclub.hk/mobile/article/article.php?cat=thezone&amp;aid=25388</a><br />\n<br />\n首先，整體黎講，有大約1/4 (25.8%) 受訪女性認同，如果第一次出街男仔冇比哂錢，就會將佢排除出戀愛對象嘅行列，呢個比例可能已經比唔少人想像中低。但更有趣嘅係，年紀越輕嘅日本女性，對於初次約會男仔有冇比哂錢呢回事就更唔著緊：10代女性中只有14%人認為男仔一定要畀哂錢、20代為22.1%、30代為21.2%，最在意呢件事嘅，反而係基本上已經退出戀愛市場嘅「50代 (36.7%)」及「60代 (31.5%)」<br />\n<br />\n我個人經驗，我咁多次約<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">靚女</span></strong></span>食飯都係女方要求aa堅持唔俾我請"},{"pid":"249053fd113f897fe5c60c620412853999419170","tid":2309863,"uid":154054,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T00:48:21.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"x-large\">係咪因為你太柒，人地唔想好似欠你野咁咋</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4aab02b7cf849d5d4f0b5c7e14b5ceb4bcc5a1d3","tid":2309863,"uid":196924,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T00:52:12.000Z","msg":"因為後生日本妹唔想你誤會"},{"pid":"90987fdc0b7a99765b7ba89efbf9fb47feca3099","tid":2309863,"uid":65328,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"249053fd113f897fe5c60c620412853999419170","tid":2309863,"uid":154054,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T00:48:21.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"x-large\">係咪因為你太柒，人地唔想好似欠你野咁咋</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2